PRACTICAL MAGIC
Type: Magical Sphere
Commands: cast, spells
See also: <spellhelp>, <help allspells>, 
  <help player documents magic>

Though you have recieved no formal training in magic, you 
have nevertheless learned to form some minor enchantments 
of everyday use.

Rumors say that a witch somewhere in the land of Gurov is
willing to teach this skill to others.
